OUR DEGREE SUSTAINABILIT Y FRAMEWORK

Governance at the business and management levels The Global Head of Sustainability (Global Head of SUS) leads

the Siemens Sustainability department. In this capacity, the Global Head of SUS reports to the CSO on all Siemens sustainability topics excluding sustainability business and related strategy topics. For the latter topics, the Global Head of SUS reports to Siemensâ€™ CEO. The Global Head of SUS is a regular member of the SSB. The Global Head of SUS regularly informs the Supervisory Board on sustainability matters.